		<hr size="1">After much work and research im going to start my monk today, or at least buy his stuff, and I have a few questions.</P><P>First, i need a nice light bag (not necessarily weight redux) for about the cost of an EE bag (bout 300p or so), i will be using this bag for food, water, bandages, and shurikens.</P><P>Second, i need to be sure that its the best strategy to put all my points into sta.</P><P>Also, i need your input on my equipment list, this is what ive been considering buying (i have about a 3k bank account)<BR>inventory<BR>ears = orc fang x2<BR>rings = jagged bands x2<BR>bracers = serp bracers x2<BR>necklace = black pearl choker<BR>waist = freeport quest sashes<BR>all other inventory slots = wus</P><P>weapons (i need the most help with this section)<BR>1hb = cane of the tranquil<BR>2hb = bamboo or adamantine bo <BR>h2h = not sure, but i want to get one of the new luclin weapons, preferably not an Ulak</P><P>Thank you in advance for your time, and feel free to offer new suggestions, but plz keep my cash limit in mind.</P><P>BTW. this character will be on E'Ci if that makes any difference to any of you.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
