		Subject:&nbsp;<b>RE: Help me out please</b></font>
		
		<a href="MB_Editmsg.asp?FID=65&FN=Monk&SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=1300239&TN=Help+me+out+please&CAT=Classes&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&MSID=1300250&PL=4&amp;action=REPLY"><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/btn_reply.gif" border="0" align="right" alt="Reply to message"></a>
