		<hr size="1">ok, i would suggest this for you</P><P>weapons - fighting batons x2, they are cheap, and are very fast and effecient for lower levels pre 35 until wu stick starts proccing.  <BR>bag - shralok pack, or herbalist pack, it seems like you have a high lvl char, with 3k to spend, so go down to cc and pick on off an herbalist, on my server they are rotting all the time so that shouldnt be a problem.<BR>i dont know the price on a shralok pack, i would think around 250pp maybe.<BR>vox bracers, not serp bracers.  AC is KING, remember that and your monk will kick ass and solo for a long time.<BR>ulthork hide collars are good, 7ac 30hps .5wt, those can be found off ulthorks in EW, or bought for around 50pp,<BR>wu armor is cool, might want to upgrade to a crystal covered shroud(which you can also pick up in crystal caverns if u decide to camp an herbalist pack, fairly common drop too)<BR>put your equip before your weight reduc bag, you can survive with a small back and wrist pouches for a while, plus is gives you more money to spend on your equipment.<BR>sta is a good point addition, along with agi, both raise ac/hp<BR>try to get 5/55 or 6/65 rings, those are awesome, high ac, high hps.</P><P>so here is the pricing on what i suggested:<BR>5ac/55hp rings:  250 a piece, 500 pair<BR>6ac/65hp rings:  300 a piece, 600 pair(if your lucky)<BR>ulthork hide collar, crystal covered shroud, herbalist pack - free<BR>vox bracers - apprx. 80pp for pair<BR>fighting batons: apprx. 800pp pair<BR>full suit of wu: 400pp ? not really sure on that<BR>total price:  apprx 1.8K, so with that much extra you can get alot more things, or swap out a cane of tranquil for one fighting baton, thatll add around 400pp. <BR>along with the person above me, go for ac/hps..they are the most important stats above all.  my monk has solo'd till 40, and is still doing so.<BR>later<BR>-Kardon, 40 Monk<BR>Xegony, The Fellowship of the Griffon<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
